    },
    {
      "name": "AK.UserIdentity API",
      "description": "User identity microservice — Keycloak-backed auth proxy.\nSwagger UI: {{identityUrl}}/swagger\n\nPre-seeded users:\n- admin / admin123 (roles: admin, user)\n- user1 / user123 (roles: user)\n\nThe Login requests auto-save the access token to {{accessToken}}.",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "Auth",
          "item": [
            {
              "name": "POST Login (User)",
              "event": [
                {
                  "listen": "test",
                  "script": {
                    "exec": [
                      "if (pm.response.code === 200) {",
                      "    var json = pm.response.json();",
                      "    pm.collectionVariables.set('accessToken', json.accessToken);",
                      "    console.log('Access token saved to {{accessToken}}');",
                      "}"
                    ],
                    "type": "text/javascript"
                  }
                }
              ],
              "request": {
                "method": "POST",
                "header": [{"key":"Content-Type","value":"application/json"}],
                "body": { "mode": "raw", "raw": "{\n  \"username\": \"user1\",\n  \"password\": \"user123\"\n}" },
                "url": { "raw": "{{identityUrl}}/api/auth/login", "host": ["{{identityUrl}}"], "path": ["api","auth","login"] }
              }
            },
            {
              "name": "POST Login (Admin)",
              "event": [
                {
                  "listen": "test",
                  "script": {
                    "exec": [
                      "if (pm.response.code === 200) {",
                      "    var json = pm.response.json();",
                      "    pm.collectionVariables.set('accessToken', json.accessToken);",
                      "    console.log('Admin access token saved to {{accessToken}}');",
                      "}"
                    ],
                    "type": "text/javascript"
                  }
                }
              ],
              "request": {
                "method": "POST",
                "header": [{"key":"Content-Type","value":"application/json"}],
                "body": { "mode": "raw", "raw": "{\n  \"username\": \"admin\",\n  \"password\": \"admin123\"\n}" },
                "url": { "raw": "{{identityUrl}}/api/auth/login", "host": ["{{identityUrl}}"], "path": ["api","auth","login"] }
              }
            },
            {
              "name": "POST Register",
              "request": {
                "method": "POST",
                "header": [{"key":"Content-Type","value":"application/json"}],
                "body": { "mode": "raw", "raw": "{\n  \"username\": \"newuser\",\n  \"email\": \"newuser@example.com\",\n  \"password\": \"SecurePass1!\",\n  \"firstName\": \"New\",\n  \"lastName\": \"User\"\n}" },
                "url": { "raw": "{{identityUrl}}/api/auth/register", "host": ["{{identityUrl}}"], "path": ["api","auth","register"] }
              }
            },
            {
              "name": "POST Refresh Token",
              "request": {
                "method": "POST",
                "header": [{"key":"Content-Type","value":"application/json"}],
                "body": { "mode": "raw", "raw": "{\n  \"refreshToken\": \"paste-refresh-token-here\"\n}" },
                "url": { "raw": "{{identityUrl}}/api/auth/refresh", "host": ["{{identityUrl}}"], "path": ["api","auth","refresh"] }
              }
            },
            {
              "name": "GET Me (current user)",
              "request": {
                "method": "GET",
                "header": [{"key":"Authorization","value":"Bearer {{accessToken}}"}],
                "url": { "raw": "{{identityUrl}}/api/auth/me", "host": ["{{identityUrl}}"], "path": ["api","auth","me"] }
              }
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "name": "Admin",
          "item": [
            {
              "name": "GET All Users (admin only)",
              "request": {
                "method": "GET",
                "header": [{"key":"Authorization","value":"Bearer {{accessToken}}"}],
                "url": { "raw": "{{identityUrl}}/api/admin/users", "host": ["{{identityUrl}}"], "path": ["api","admin","users"] }
              }
            },
            {
              "name": "POST Assign Role (admin only)",
              "request": {
                "method": "POST",
                "header": [{"key":"Content-Type","value":"application/json"},{"key":"Authorization","value":"Bearer {{accessToken}}"}],
                "body": { "mode": "raw", "raw": "{\n  \"role\": \"admin\"\n}" },
                "url": { "raw": "{{identityUrl}}/api/admin/users/replace-with-user-id/roles", "host": ["{{identityUrl}}"], "path": ["api","admin","users","replace-with-user-id","roles"] }
              }
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "name": "GET Identity Health Check",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET", "header": [],
            "url": { "raw": "{{identityUrl}}/health", "host": ["{{identityUrl}}"], "path": ["health"] }
          }
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "name": "AK.Payments API",
      "description": "Payment processing microservice — REST/HTTP.\nSwagger UI: {{paymentsUrl}}/swagger\n\nIDOR-safe: userId is always derived from the JWT. No userId in paths or bodies.\nRazorpay two-step flow: POST /initiate → POST /verify\nTest cards: 4111 1111 1111 1111 (Visa), 5267 3169 4984 2643 (Mastercard). OTP: 1234 1234\nPaymentMethod: 1=Card, 2=SavedCard, 3=UPI, 4=NetBanking",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "POST Initiate Payment",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "exec": [
                  "if (pm.response.code === 200) {",
                  "    var json = pm.response.json();",
                  "    pm.collectionVariables.set('paymentId', json.id);",
                  "    pm.collectionVariables.set('razorpayOrderId', json.razorpayOrderId);",
                  "    console.log('paymentId saved: ' + json.id);",
                  "}"
                ],
                "type": "text/javascript"
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [{"key":"Content-Type","value":"application/json"},{"key":"Authorization","value":"Bearer {{accessToken}}"}],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"orderId\": \"{{orderId}}\",\n  \"orderNumber\": \"ORD-20260426-ABCD1234\",\n  \"amount\": 199998,\n  \"method\": 1\n}",
              "options": {"raw":{"language":"json"}}
            },
            "url": { "raw": "{{paymentsUrl}}/api/payments/initiate", "host": ["{{paymentsUrl}}"], "path": ["api","payments","initiate"] }
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "POST Verify Payment",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [{"key":"Content-Type","value":"application/json"},{"key":"Authorization","value":"Bearer {{accessToken}}"}],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"paymentId\": \"{{paymentId}}\",\n  \"razorpayOrderId\": \"{{razorpayOrderId}}\",\n  \"razorpayPaymentId\": \"{{razorpayPaymentId}}\",\n  \"razorpaySignature\": \"{{razorpaySignature}}\"\n}",
              "options": {"raw":{"language":"json"}}
            },
            "url": { "raw": "{{paymentsUrl}}/api/payments/verify", "host": ["{{paymentsUrl}}"], "path": ["api","payments","verify"] }
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "GET My Payments",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [{"key":"Authorization","value":"Bearer {{accessToken}}"}],
            "url": { "raw": "{{paymentsUrl}}/api/payments/me", "host": ["{{paymentsUrl}}"], "path": ["api","payments","me"] }
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "GET Payment by ID",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [{"key":"Authorization","value":"Bearer {{accessToken}}"}],
            "url": { "raw": "{{paymentsUrl}}/api/payments/{{paymentId}}", "host": ["{{paymentsUrl}}"], "path": ["api","payments","{{paymentId}}"] }
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "GET Payment by Order",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [{"key":"Authorization","value":"Bearer {{accessToken}}"}],
            "url": { "raw": "{{paymentsUrl}}/api/payments/order/{{orderId}}", "host": ["{{paymentsUrl}}"], "path": ["api","payments","order","{{orderId}}"] }
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "POST Save Card",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [{"key":"Content-Type","value":"application/json"},{"key":"Authorization","value":"Bearer {{accessToken}}"}],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"razorpayCustomerId\": \"{{razorpayCustomerId}}\",\n  \"razorpayPaymentId\": \"{{razorpayPaymentId}}\",\n  \"customerName\": \"Test User\",\n  \"customerEmail\": \"user1@example.com\",\n  \"customerContact\": \"+919876543210\"\n}",
              "options": {"raw":{"language":"json"}}
            },
            "url": { "raw": "{{paymentsUrl}}/api/payments/cards/save", "host": ["{{paymentsUrl}}"], "path": ["api","payments","cards","save"] }
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "GET Saved Cards",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [{"key":"Authorization","value":"Bearer {{accessToken}}"}],
            "url": { "raw": "{{paymentsUrl}}/api/payments/cards", "host": ["{{paymentsUrl}}"], "path": ["api","payments","cards"] }
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "DELETE Saved Card",
          "request": {
            "method": "DELETE",
            "header": [{"key":"Authorization","value":"Bearer {{accessToken}}"}],
            "url": { "raw": "{{paymentsUrl}}/api/payments/cards/{{cardId}}", "host": ["{{paymentsUrl}}"], "path": ["api","payments","cards","{{cardId}}"] }
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "[401] Initiate Payment — No Auth",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [{"key":"Content-Type","value":"application/json"}],
            "description": "Expect 401 Unauthorized — no Bearer token provided",
            "body": { "mode": "raw", "raw": "{\n  \"orderId\": \"{{orderId}}\",\n  \"orderNumber\": \"ORD-20260426-ABCD1234\",\n  \"amount\": 199998,\n  \"method\": 1\n}", "options": {"raw":{"language":"json"}} },
            "url": { "raw": "{{paymentsUrl}}/api/payments/initiate", "host": ["{{paymentsUrl}}"], "path": ["api","payments","initiate"] }
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "[400] Initiate Payment — Missing Amount",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [{"key":"Content-Type","value":"application/json"},{"key":"Authorization","value":"Bearer {{accessToken}}"}],
            "description": "Expect 400 Bad Request — amount is required",
            "body": { "mode": "raw", "raw": "{\n  \"orderId\": \"{{orderId}}\",\n  \"orderNumber\": \"ORD-20260426-ABCD1234\",\n  \"method\": 1\n}", "options": {"raw":{"language":"json"}} },
            "url": { "raw": "{{paymentsUrl}}/api/payments/initiate", "host": ["{{paymentsUrl}}"], "path": ["api","payments","initiate"] }
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "[400] Initiate Payment — Zero Amount",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [{"key":"Content-Type","value":"application/json"},{"key":"Authorization","value":"Bearer {{accessToken}}"}],
            "description": "Expect 400 Bad Request — amount must be > 0",
            "body": { "mode": "raw", "raw": "{\n  \"orderId\": \"{{orderId}}\",\n  \"orderNumber\": \"ORD-20260426-ABCD1234\",\n  \"amount\": 0,\n  \"method\": 1\n}", "options": {"raw":{"language":"json"}} },
            "url": { "raw": "{{paymentsUrl}}/api/payments/initiate", "host": ["{{paymentsUrl}}"], "path": ["api","payments","initiate"] }
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "[400] Verify Payment — Invalid Signature",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [{"key":"Content-Type","value":"application/json"},{"key":"Authorization","value":"Bearer {{accessToken}}"}],
            "description": "Expect 400 — HMAC-SHA256 signature mismatch",
            "body": { "mode": "raw", "raw": "{\n  \"paymentId\": \"{{paymentId}}\",\n  \"razorpayOrderId\": \"{{razorpayOrderId}}\",\n  \"razorpayPaymentId\": \"pay_invalid_test\",\n  \"razorpaySignature\": \"invalidsignature123abc\"\n}", "options": {"raw":{"language":"json"}} },
            "url": { "raw": "{{paymentsUrl}}/api/payments/verify", "host": ["{{paymentsUrl}}"], "path": ["api","payments","verify"] }
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "[401] Get My Payments — No Auth",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET", "header": [],
            "description": "Expect 401 Unauthorized",
            "url": { "raw": "{{paymentsUrl}}/api/payments/me", "host": ["{{paymentsUrl}}"], "path": ["api","payments","me"] }
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "[401] Get Saved Cards — No Auth",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET", "header": [],
            "description": "Expect 401 Unauthorized",
            "url": { "raw": "{{paymentsUrl}}/api/payments/cards", "host": ["{{paymentsUrl}}"], "path": ["api","payments","cards"] }
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "[400] Save Card — Missing RazorpayCustomerId",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [{"key":"Content-Type","value":"application/json"},{"key":"Authorization","value":"Bearer {{accessToken}}"}],
            "description": "Expect 400 — razorpayCustomerId is required",
            "body": { "mode": "raw", "raw": "{\n  \"razorpayPaymentId\": \"pay_test\",\n  \"customerName\": \"Test User\",\n  \"customerEmail\": \"user1@example.com\",\n  \"customerContact\": \"+919876543210\"\n}", "options": {"raw":{"language":"json"}} },
            "url": { "raw": "{{paymentsUrl}}/api/payments/cards/save", "host": ["{{paymentsUrl}}"], "path": ["api","payments","cards","save"] }
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "GET Payments Health Check",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET", "header": [],
            "url": { "raw": "{{paymentsUrl}}/health", "host": ["{{paymentsUrl}}"], "path": ["health"] }
          }
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "name": "AK.Notification API",
      "description": "Notification microservice — REST/HTTP (event-driven).\nSwagger UI: {{notificationUrl}}/swagger\n\nNotifications are created automatically by consuming integration events from RabbitMQ:\n- UserRegisteredIntegrationEvent → welcome email\n- OrderCreatedIntegrationEvent → order confirmation\n- OrderConfirmedIntegrationEvent → stock confirmed\n- OrderCancelledIntegrationEvent → cancellation notice\n- PaymentSucceededIntegrationEvent → payment receipt\n- PaymentFailedIntegrationEvent → payment failure alert\n\nIDOR-safe: users can only read their own notifications. Admin endpoint returns all.",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "GET My Notifications",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [{"key":"Authorization","value":"Bearer {{accessToken}}"}],
            "url": { "raw": "{{notificationUrl}}/api/notifications?page=1&pageSize=20", "host": ["{{notificationUrl}}"], "path": ["api","notifications"], "query": [{"key":"page","value":"1"},{"key":"pageSize","value":"20"}] }
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "GET Notification by ID",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [{"key":"Authorization","value":"Bearer {{accessToken}}"}],
            "url": { "raw": "{{notificationUrl}}/api/notifications/{{notificationId}}", "host": ["{{notificationUrl}}"], "path": ["api","notifications","{{notificationId}}"] }
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "GET All Notifications (admin only)",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [{"key":"Authorization","value":"Bearer {{accessToken}}"}],
            "description": "Requires admin role. Returns all notifications across all users.",
            "url": { "raw": "{{notificationUrl}}/api/notifications/admin?page=1&pageSize=20", "host": ["{{notificationUrl}}"], "path": ["api","notifications","admin"], "query": [{"key":"page","value":"1"},{"key":"pageSize","value":"20"}] }
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "GET Notification Health Check",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET", "header": [],
            "url": { "raw": "{{notificationUrl}}/health", "host": ["{{notificationUrl}}"], "path": ["health"] }
          }
        }
      ]
    }
  ]
}
